{
  "stem": "11174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That a soldier is marching up and down that house on the sidewalk, watching that store, because they had put in so much money-- so much material there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a store with a fortune of money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you have-- I got stupid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I watched him, somehow, when they did something to me, the fear was over, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, somehow the normal-- I wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If there was nothing happened, I wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I waited.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he marched this way, I snuck into that yard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a fence with boards around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I snuck into that yard, and I-- Yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where they put their valuables, they told me like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There is-- there was a hole and under the hole was boards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on the boards was-- was sand, again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was some box, all the sandbox, on top of that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They move that away and they put it there, so that's where I'm going to find it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The soldier marches up and down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'm inside looking for that money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What happened, what we found out later, I'll tell you how, is that the Germans had somehow moved that sandbox.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was maybe 12 feet away from that spot, so I didn't find the real spot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My [INAUDIBLE] finding was that box with the sand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I go down and I dig and I dig.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] all I had on me was a pair of pants and a little sweater and a beret, no beard.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans had-- I had already a beard, but the Germans had cut off half, so I went and cut off the rest.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How'd they cut that off?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When was this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They go over with the machine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zoom, zoom, zoom.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
